snippet.textDisplay: Faltu hoise. The first song should have been a tidal wave. Missed opportunity. Nasek nasek? What is nasek nasek. I speak bangla and i don't understand anything. I live in Bangladesh and I don't know a single person who speaks this language or even knew that this language exists within our borders. Yes you can can call it a Bangladeshi song but you can't call it a Bangla song. The show is called Coke Studio Bangla.. Not Coke Studio Hajong . Don't get me wrong - these minority languages are most welcome but only once the foundation of the show is strong. My suggestion is to start with Ami Bangla'y gaan gai but with a fresh take. Thanks for your time. Don't fight for no reason. I'm trying to contribute towards progress.
